[I] COIN-OR BiCePS Linear Integer Solver (BLIS)

[T] This is the BiCePS Linear Integer Solver (BLIS), a parallel solver for mixed integer linear programs that is implemented on top of the BiCePS layer of the CHiPPS framework.

